item.description:
Join us for dinner and drinks at CACTUS JACKS, 782 Willow St Manchester, NH.
(across from Stop and Shop)

A casual meetup for us to get to know each other and maybe meet you for the first time. We had a great dinner our last meetup here and the food is good. The conversations never stop, and we shouldn't need to worry about the weather.




Directions and menu:CJ's Great West Grill Manchester

Restaurant is across the street from the Stop and Shop Plaza. Meet in the bar lounge area.
item.how_to_find_us: 603-477-5116 Diane. I'll have a Meetup table sign in the back of the bar area.
